<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style>
* {
	font-family: "HelveticaNeue-Light", "Helvetica Neue Light",
		"Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "Lucida Grande", sans-serif;
}

</style>
<body>
	<div style="width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
		<div style="width: 200px; height: 50px;">
			<img src="http://www.tutorcan.com/resource/logo.png" width="100%" height="100%" />
		</div>
		<div
			style="height: 80px; line-height: 80px; font-size: 22px; text-align: center; background-color: #ddd; margin-top: 20px;">Thank
			you for registering TutorCan!</div>
		<div
			style="font-size: 16px; background-color: #f2f2f2; padding: 14px;">
			<p>Dear ${username},</p>
			<p>You have successfully created your account at TutorCan. Please
				click the following button to complete your registration and make
				full use of TutorCan's function.</p>

			<p>
				<a href="http://www.tutorcan.com/activate.html?uuid=${uuid}"><button
						style="-webkit-border-radius: 8; -moz-border-radius: 8; border-radius: 8px; font-family: Arial; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; background: #54b4f5; padding: 7px 15px 7px 15px; text-decoration: none; border: none;">Activation
						Link</button></a>
			</p>
			<p>If the button doesn't work, please copy the following link to
				your browser's address bar.</p>
			<p style="color: #14f; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">http://www.tutorcan.com/activate.html?uuid=${uuid}</p>
			<div style="height: 20px;">&nbsp;</div>
			<p style="font-weight: bold;">Not your operation?</p>
			<p>
				You can safely disregard this email. If you are interested in online
				tutoring, please pay a visit to <a href="#">www.tutorcan.com</a> and
				we are sure you will like it.
			</p>

			<p>Best,</p>
			<p>The TutorCan Team</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>